stateDiagram-v2
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% STATE — options quick-ref
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% Header:      stateDiagram | stateDiagram-v2
%% Transitions: StateA --> StateB  ·  StateA --> StateB : label
%%              [*] --> StateA  (entry)  ·  StateA --> [*]  (exit)
%% Blocks:      state Name { … }  (composite)
%% Specials:    state id <<choice>> · <<fork>> · <<join>>
%%              state "label" as id  ·  state id
%% Config:      direction LR  (ignored)  ·  note text  (discarded)
%% Frontmatter: --- yaml block --- (before header)
%% Comments:    %% text  (stripped before parse — safe on any line)
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Processing : order_placed
    Processing --> Authorized : authorize [amount > 0]
    Processing --> Failed : authorize [amount <= 0]
    Failed --> [*]
    state Processing {
        [*] --> Validating
        Validating --> Charging : valid
        Charging --> [*]
    }
    state choice1 <<choice>>
    Authorized --> choice1
    choice1 --> Completed : [full payment]
    choice1 --> PartialPay : [partial]
    PartialPay --> Completed : remaining paid
    Completed --> Refunding : refund_requested
    Refunding --> Refunded : process_refund
    Refunded --> [*]
    Completed --> [*]
